Emily", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_002", "subject": "Q3 Project Status Update", "from": "mark.brown@mediconn.com", "from_name": "Mark Brown", "to": ["emily.patel@mediconn.com"], "cc": ["lucas.anderson@mediconn.com"], "date": "2022-09-22 14:25:00", "body": "Hi Emily, 

